// SidePanel.jsx
import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { Card, Form, ButtonGroup, ToggleButton, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';

function SidePanel({ onUpdateSettings }) {
  const [source, setSource] = useState('real'); // 'real' or 'ai'
  const [voiceApi, setVoiceApi] = useState('browser'); // 'browser', 'openai', 'google', 'minimax', 'silent'
  const [answerMode, setAnswerMode] = useState('text'); // 'text' or 'voice'
  const [evaluationApi, setEvaluationApi] = useState('zhipuai'); // 'zhipuai' or 'openai'

  const handleUpdateSettings = () => {
    onUpdateSettings({ source, voiceApi, answerMode, evaluationApi });
  };

  return (
    <Card>
      <Card.Body>
        <Form>
          {/* 题目来源选择 */}
          <Form.Group>
            <Form.Label>题目来源</Form.Label>
            <ButtonGroup toggle>
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="source"
                value="real"
                checked={source === 'real'}
                onChange={(e) => setSource(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                真题
              </ToggleButton>
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="source"
                value="ai"
                checked={source === 'ai'}
                onChange={(e) => setSource(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                AI模拟题
              </ToggleButton>
            </ButtonGroup>
          </Form.Group>

          {/* 语音播放方式选择 */}
          <Form.Group>
            <Form.Label>语音播放方式</Form.Label>
            <ButtonGroup toggle>
              {/* 额外的选项可以根据需求添加 */}
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="voiceApi"
                value="browser"
                checked={voiceApi === 'browser'}
                onChange={(e) => setVoiceApi(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                浏览器
              </ToggleButton>
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="voiceApi"
                value="openai"
                checked={voiceApi === 'openai'}
                onChange={(e) => setVoiceApi(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                OpenAI
              </ToggleButton>
              {/* ...其他选项 */}
            </ButtonGroup>
          </Form.Group>

          {/* 回答方式选择 */}
          <Form.Group>
            <Form.Label>回答方式</Form.Label>
            <ButtonGroup toggle>
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="answerMode"
                value="text"
                checked={answerMode === 'text'}
                onChange={(e) => setAnswerMode(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                文本输入
              </ToggleButton>
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="answerMode"
                value="voice"
                checked={answerMode === 'voice'}
                onChange={(e) => setAnswerMode(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                语音答题
              </ToggleButton>
            </ButtonGroup>
          </Form.Group>

          {/* 评价API选择 */}
          <Form.Group>
            <Form.Label>生成评价的API</Form.Label>
            <ButtonGroup toggle>
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="evaluationApi"
                value="zhipuai"
                checked={evaluationApi === 'zhipuai'}
                onChange={(e) => setEvaluationApi(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                智普AI
              </ToggleButton>
              <ToggleButton
                type="radio"
                variant="secondary"
                name="evaluationApi"
                value="openai"
                checked={evaluationApi === 'openai'}
                onChange={(e) => setEvaluationApi(e.currentTarget.value)}
              >
                OpenAI
              </ToggleButton>
            </ButtonGroup>
          </Form.Group>

          <Button onClick={handleUpdateSettings} variant="primary">
            应用设置
          </Button>
        </Form>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>
  );
}

export default SidePanel;
